Alle Dateien muessen im Verzeichnis /home/ticker/ liegen.

install_/remove_ticker...
+ ticker.cron

install_ticker_ ...
installs a cron job, that looks for a running ticker, and starts one,
if no ticker was found.

remove_ticker_...
removes the ticker control script from the crontab



install_/remove_activated...

installs and removes the activated.cron script to and from the 
crontab.
The activated.cron script is called every six hours and looks for not
activated accounts. If these accounts are older than a certain
time span, they are deleted with the script deletePlayer.script.php



